<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA46">
<l>payiṉṟa taraṅkan tirukkōṭṭi paṉṉāḷ</l>
<l>payiṉṟatuvum vēṅkaṭamē paṉṉāḷ – payiṉṟa</l>
<l>taṇitikaḻuñ cōlai yaṇinīr malaiyē</l>
<l>maṇitikaḻum vaṇṭaṭakkai māl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is resident in [Tiruv]araṅkam [and] Tirukkōṭṭi and since many days</l>
<l>is he resident in Vēṅkaṭam, since many days he is resident</l>
<l>in ornate glittering Cōlai [and] on the decorative Nīrmalai</l>
<l>– Māl with liberal broad hands who glitters [like] a sapphire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
